These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, metal, folk
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of electronic is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the fan of electronic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | jazz | folk | metal |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, amaryllis, begonia, rose
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsdaffodil is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Flower   | rose    | daffodil | begonia | amaryllis    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, videographer, paramedic, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. the photographer is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the videographer##3
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4
6. the videographer is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job          | photographer | paramedic | videographer    | librarian      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
House: futuristic, colonial, ranch-style, art-deco
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the colonial house is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House         | art-deco | futuristic | colonial | ranch-style |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, orange, emerald, fuchsia
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, indian, russian
1. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the russian##1
2. the australian is the person who likes fuchsia##1
3. the indian is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes emerald is in an odd position##4
6. the american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Color   | orange  | azure    | emerald   | fuchsia       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

