.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, mystery, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, photography, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | mystery | family    |
| Hobby     | rock-climbing | photography  | video-games     | card-games |

