.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, hiking, video-games, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is baking and the owner of the goat##2
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Hobby   | hiking | baking      | puzzles | video-games |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

