.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, bus, boat
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the car and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Transport    | boat     | car | scooter     | bus  |

