.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, blood-red, green
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, electronic, jazz
1. the person who likes ebony is the fan of jazz##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the fan of jazz is between the fan of disco and the person who likes blood-red##2
4. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | apricot       | blood-red   | ebony | green |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | dubstep | jazz        | disco    |

