.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, zombie, horror, disaster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, sailing, disaster-polo
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is disaster-polo##1
4. the person who's sport is disaster-polo is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | disaster   | zombie      | horror      |
| Sport      | cycling | sailing | disaster-polo | biathlon |

