2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
4. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Sport   | sailing | lacrosse | badminton | surfing  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

