.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, pear, potato, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, nigerian, turkish
1. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
3. the japanese is the person eating potato##1
4. the nigerian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
5. the japanese is between the turkish and the nigerian##2
6. the person eating pear is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food         | avocado   | potato | peas | pear    |
| Nationality   | nigerian | japanese  | turkish     | american |

