.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, water
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, polish, indian, canadian
1. the polish is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
4. the indian is on the left of the canadian##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the indian is in an even position##4
7. the thai is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Nationality       | polish  | indian | canadian | thai  |

