.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, software-developer
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, dancing, photography, camping
1. the manager is in an even position##4
2. the manager is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the entrepreneur and the person who's hobby is reading##2
4. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the software-developer##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | entrepreneur | pilot   | software-developer | manager |
| Hobby   | camping          | dancing | reading         | photography  |

 